  <p>StoryIt may share data with trusted partners to help perform statistical analysis, send you email or postal mail, provide customer support, or arrange for deliveries. All such third parties are prohibited from using your personal information except to provide these services to StoryIt, and they are required to maintain the confidentiality of your information. </p>
  <p>StoryIt may disclose your personal information, without notice, if required to do so by law or in the good faith belief that such action is necessary to: (a) conform to the edicts of the law or comply with legal process served on StoryIt or the site; (b) protect and defend the rights or property of StoryIt; and/or (c) act under exigent circumstances to protect the personal safety of users of StoryIt, or the public. </p>
